** 5-Transistor OTA — SkyWater 130nm (sky130A)
** Classic Miller OTA: differential pair + active load + tail source
**
**         VDD
**          |
**     M3 --+-- M4
**     |         |
**  net1       vout
**     |         |
**     M1 --+-- M2
**          |
**         net3
**          |
**         M5
**          |
**         VSS

.subckt opamp vip vin vout vdd vss

** PMOS active load (current mirror)
XM3 net1 net1 vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W=4u L=0.5u nf=1
XM4 vout net1 vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W=4u L=0.5u nf=1

** NMOS differential pair
XM1 net1 vip net3 vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=2u L=0.5u nf=1
XM2 vout vin net3 vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=2u L=0.5u nf=1

** NMOS tail current source (gate tied to bias)
XM5 net3 vbias vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=4u L=1u nf=1

** Simple self-bias: diode-connected NMOS mirrors tail current
XM6 vbias vbias vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W=4u L=1u nf=1
Ibias vdd vbias 20u

.ends opamp
